OL,4,FOur readers have flagged up a few
OL,5,Ftechnical blips that occurred during
OL,6,Ftoday's news coverage of the
OL,7,Fannouncement of the new Prime Minister.
OL,9,FA few minutes into BBC One's special
OL,10,Fprogramme at 12pm, a live piece by Huw
OL,11,FEdwards in Downing Street fell off air
OL,12,Fand was replaced briefly by colour
OL,13,Fbars. Studio-based Joanna Gosling
OL,14,Fquickly stepped in.
OL,16,FOn Politics Live on BBC Two, a live
OL,17,Fshot of 10 Downing Street abruptly cut
OL,18,Fto colour bars, with a GB News logo
OL,19,Foverlaid. GB News would've been part of
OL,20,Fa pool of broadcasters providing live
OL,21,Fpictures.
OL,3,CTimeline: 2022 Week 36
