OL,4,FAnd over on the ITV Lunchtime News, a
OL,5,Flive conversation in front of 10
OL,6,FDowning Street, between presenter Nina
OL,7,FHossain and political editor Robert
OL,8,FPeston, came to an unexpected end when
OL,9,Fthe line was lost. We were taken back
OL,10,Fto the studio, where Geraint Vincent
OL,11,Fwas on standby.
OL,13,FThe opening seconds of tonight's
OL,14,Fedition of the ITV Evening News has
OL,15,Fbeen viewed tens of thousands of times
OL,16,Fon social media.
OL,3,CTimeline: 2022 Week 36
