OL,4,FPresenter Mary Nightingale was
OL,5,Fproviding the opening link to camera,
OL,6,Flive from Downing Street, when someone
OL,7,Fbriefly passed in front of the camera.
OL,8,FA slight wobble in Mary's voice was
OL,9,Falso noted by viewers.
OL,11,FExtended coverage of the appointment of
OL,12,FLiz Truss as the new UK prime minister
OL,13,Fmeant that today's edition of Pointless
OL,14,Fmoved from BBC One to BBC Two.
OL,16,FOn BBC Two Wales, a minor mishap with
OL,17,Fthe playout schedule meant we got a few
OL,18,Fseconds of BBC One's one rolling news
OL,19,Fcoverage, rather than the start of
OL,20,FPointless.
