OL,4,FThe issue was quickly rectified.
OL,6,FOn the day that Liz Truss was formally
OL,7,Finstalled as the UK prime minister,
OL,8,FNewsnight produced a short montage of
OL,9,Fimages from the day's events,
OL,10,Faccompanied by its rarely used closing
OL,11,Ftheme.
OL,13,FOrdinarily, the programme's opening
OL,14,Ftheme is also used at the end of the
OL,15,Fprogramme.
